release_notes.en-US:
Here what's new in this version:
*) Better English localization (Thanks to Matt Farey);
*) Better Italian localization using letters like with accents;
*) Added Swedish localization (Thanks to Hans Johansson);
*) Added Spanish localization (Thanks to Emiliano Deza);
*) Better localization support for non standard  ASCII characters;
*) Now "Preseve subfolder structure" is active only when "Include subfolders" is active;
*) Better SmartSave button on the toolbar: now when you click you can either configure smartsave or perform the export.
*) By default the SmartSave button isn't visible on the toolbar;
*) When creating filename the ":" will be reaplced by "-" beacuse some OS (i.e. Windows) doesn't support it!
*) By deafult the basefolder point to the home directory (%HOME% on Windows, $HOME on Unix and Macs)
*) Checked minor bugs;
